sentences: Dennis "Seregor" Droomers (born 27 October 1980) is a vocalist, guitarist, artist, and songwriter.

Before Carach Angren, Droomers played bass and was the vocalist for Inger Indolia from 1996-2001 and was the vocalist for Vaultage from 2003-2005 with fellow Carach Angren member Clemens "Ardek" Wijers on keyboards.
